	c) the period in the case of any person falling within paragraph (1)(d) is the period starting with the date of registration with Jobcentre Plus and ending on the day on which the person is next due to attend in accordance with regulation 23 or regulation 23A or on the date on which the period calculated in accordance with regulation 59(2) or 60(2) or sub-paragraph (b) would have expired, whichever first occurs; 
